General.Name: M3 Mining Ltd
General.Description: M3 Mining Limited engages in the exploration and evaluation of mineral resources in Australia. The company primarily explores for copper and gold deposits. It holds a 100% interest in the Edjudina project comprising six licenses located approximately 150 km north east of Kalgoorlie in the Eastern Goldfields, Western Australia; and the Victoria Bore project located in the Pilbara region of Western Australia. The company was incorporated in 2020 and is headquartered in Perth, Australia.
